	<div class="box">
   <p class="heading">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</p>
   <div class="container">
   <div class="faqs">
      <details>
         <summary>How do I register with Apnashow ?</summary>
        <p class="text">Oh, that's easy as pie!
Just go to our website or application and click on the Sign-in option. You can either sign up with a Google+, Facebook or the best option is the mobile number of your choice. And its done!</p>
      </details>
      <details>
         <summary>Where do I find Coupons on Apnashow?</summary>
         <p class="text">Coupons can be selected after a successful booking. You can select them using the link shared in your confirmation email. You can also find an option to add coupons under 'Purchase History'.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
         <summary>What is the age limit for children to buy a ticket?</summary>
         <p class="text">Below are the age criteria to buy a ticket. Just to keep you informed, for an "A" adult movie this will not be levied.

Mumbai: Children aged 2 years and above will require a ticket for all cinemas in this region (Including KT Vision Vasai).    

For all Carnival cinemas, children aged 3 years and above require a full ticket to watch a movie.</p>
      </details>
     <details>
       <summary>Booked tickets for a movie but the show was cancelled. Please help!</summary>
       <p class="text">Due to these trying times, it may take a maximum of 15 working days for the amount to reflect in your account. We are leaving no stone unturned to ensure the amount reaches you soon.</p>
     </details>
     <details>
       <summary>How long is the Coupon valid?</summary>
       <p class="text">The Coupons are valid from the date of the Movie till days specified for the brand campaign. 

The Start date and Expiry date for the Coupon will be clearly displayed while picking up the coupon. 

